dc_title_s: Addresses and Driveways Washburn County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents addresses (points) and driveways (lines) for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Washburn_Addresses_2021' and 'Washburn_Driveways_2021.'Addresses: [This data set consists of digital map files containing addressing or site access information obtained by a combination of lab work using aerial imagery and gps collection of address sign. Features contained in the data set include all site access points countywide and associated attributes. Site access points sometimes are referred to as addresses, however this data typically represents the GPS location of the address sign. The Washburn County Land Information Office plans to maintain this digital data in ESRI's ArcGIS geodatabase environment using ArcMap tools. Some of the data was developed using field data collection techniques and field data collection will be used extensively to maintain the data. There are attributes in the data documenting each record source.]Driveways: [This data set consists of digital map files containing driveways obtained by conducting lab work using aerial imagery. Features contained in the data set include numerous driveways that are necessary to provide information to help connect or point the way between the site access point and the primary structure]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://co.washburn.wi.us/gis-data-downloads/
